home health services, skilled nursing 
services, inpatient rehabilitation services, 
and inpatient hospital services furnished by 
a long-term care hospital. (v) Other services the Secretary determines 
appropriate. (d)  EPISODE OF CARE. (i)  IN GENERAL. Subject to clause (ii), the term episode of care means, with respect to an applicable condition and an 
