physicians services has the meaning given 

such term in section 1861 (q).(f) PILOT PROGRAM. The term pilot 

program means the pilot program under this 

section. 

 (g) PROVIDER OF SERVICES. The term 
provider of services has the meaning given 
such term in section 1861 (u). (h) READMISSION. The term readmission 
has the meaning given such term in section 
1886 (q)</p><p>(5)(e). 
