 (B) DEVELOPMENTAL PHASE.</p>

<p>(1) DETERMINATION OF PATIENT ASSESSMENT 
INSTRUMENT. The Secretary shall determine 
which patient assessment instrument (such as the 
Continuity Assessment Record and Evaluation</p>

<p>(CARE) tool) shall be used under the pilot program 
