of providers of services and suppliers, including 
a hospital, a physician group, a skilled nursing 
facility, and a home health agency, who are otherwise 
participating under this title, may submit 
an application to the Secretary to provide 
applicable services to applicable individuals 
under this section. 
 (B) REQUIREMENTS. The Secretary 
shall develop requirements for entities to participate 
in the pilot program under this section. 
